    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for COU2 VAD hemolysis prediction is accepted for regulatory submission with documented deficiencies. All 13 credibility factors were assessed; achieved levels fall below required levels for 11 of 13 factors, reflecting the high demands of MRL 5. Experiments were performed across five operating points and results were compared against experimental hemolysis index measurements. The package is accepted as a complete credibility assessment record that transparently documents gaps, enabling the regulatory reviewer to make an informed determination. Deficiencies are logged for remediation in the next design cycle.",
